data.title: My Orange Clerk Home
data.text:
Welcome to the Orange County Court Hearing Calendar. To make your court hearing search as easy as possible, be aware of the following:

This search tool is specific for quick access to find a court hearing date.

Search results can be sorted by clicking on column headings.

This tool provides a court date and location.

This tool does not provide access to past hearings.

This tool does not provide results for payments or other active cases.

Court dates and locations can change at the last minute.

Cancelled Hearings are indicated by Status.

Juvenile cases are not displayed due to confidentiality.

At least one data field is required to be filled in to return a result, when searching by name, both First and Last name are required.
